Adds new datasets to Arena

Source: R/arena.R
push_dataset.Rd

Adds data frame to create exploratory data analysis plots

push_dataset(arena, dataset, target, label)

Arguments

arena

live or static arena object
dataset

data frame used for EDA plots
target

name of target variable
label

label of dataset

Value

Updated arena object

Examples

library("DALEX")
library("arenar")
library("dplyr", quietly=TRUE, warn.conflicts = FALSE)
# create live arena with only one dataset
apartments <- DALEX::apartments
arena <- create_arena(live=TRUE) %>% push_dataset(apartments, "m2.price", "apartment")
print(arena)

#> ===== Live Arena Summary =====
#> Observations: 
#> Variables: construction.year, surface, floor, no.rooms, district
#> Models: 
#> Datasets: apartment
#> Remember to start server with run_server(arena)
# add another dataset
HR <- DALEX::HR
arena <- arena %>% push_dataset(HR, "status", "HR")
print(arena)

#> ===== Live Arena Summary =====
#> Observations: 
#> Variables: construction.year, surface, floor, no.rooms, district, gender and 4 more
#> Models: 
#> Datasets: apartment, HR
#> Remember to start server with run_server(arena)
